<h3>Radiation and Cloudiness</h3>
Due to the above mentioned block pressure pattern over Europe a rather unique pattern can be seen in the anomaly figures of radiation and cloud cover.
Over the western Mediterranean an extreme negative anomaly in radiation (and a large positive anomaly in cloud cover with record low sunshine number in Spain) occured while large parts of western and central Europe registered their sunniest april weeks in history.
